SETTINGS REQUIRED FOR HAVING A STEADY POSTMAN INTEGRATION SYSTEM:
1) Jdk version 8 with 
2) Jenkins version 2.319.3

Ways to execute Postman collections:
1) Copying JSon link from sharing option
2) Exporting collection and running json collection generated
3) Using Newman with the Postman API: https://www.npmjs.com/package/newman#using-newman-with-the-postman-api

when executing Postman collections (stored in Github) from Jenkins, look at png files "POSTMANCollectionsStoredInGITHUBAndJENKINS" and "POSTMANCollectionsStoredInGITHUBAndJENKINS2"
